OL,3,CGuernsey sees nearly 50% rise in
OL,4,Creported sexual offences
OL,6,FThere was nearly a 50% rise in
OL,7,Freported sexual offences in Guernsey
OL,8,Flast year, according to the island's
OL,9,Fpolice force.
OL,11,FThere were 232 reports of sexual
OL,12,Fcrimes made to the police in 2024, up
OL,13,Ffrom 159 the year before - an increase
OL,14,Fof 46%.
OL,16,FOf those crimes reported to officers,
OL,17,Fthere were 67 sexual assaults and 39
OL,18,Frape offences. The police also
OL,19,Freceived 31 reports of sexual
OL,20,Fcommunications with a child.
