OL,3,CGuernsey sees nearly 50% rise in
OL,4,Creported sexual offences
OL,6,FThe figures are part of Guernsey
OL,7,FPolice's annual report which breaks
OL,8,Fdown the crimes reported across the
OL,9,Fbailiwick.
OL,11,FActing Det Ch Insp Ian Tanner said:
OL,12,F"Guernsey Police do take these
OL,13,Foffences very seriously and we will
OL,14,Fthrow our resources at investigating
OL,15,Fthese matters and try and get that
OL,16,Fconviction.
