OL,3,CGuernsey sees nearly 50% rise in
OL,4,Creported sexual offences
OL,6,F"We need to make sure that people do
OL,7,Fhave that confidence in us, because
OL,8,Fit's a traumatic experience, first of
OL,9,Fall when it originally happened and
OL,10,Fthen the reporting process can appear
OL,11,Fquite daunting."
OL,13,FPoppy Murray, who runs charity
OL,14,FSafetyNet, said: "The scale of crimes
OL,15,Flike this have been massively
OL,16,Fmisunderstood for so long. These
OL,17,Ffigures will help show there is
OL,18,Fgreater awareness now of what women go
OL,19,Fthrough.
