OL,3,CGuernsey sees nearly 50% rise in
OL,4,Creported sexual offences
OL,6,F"There's still a long way to go in
OL,7,Fterms of ensuring all incidents are
OL,8,Freported but hopefully this acts as a
OL,9,Fwake up call to the community."
OL,11,FThe bailiwick also saw an increase in
OL,12,Fthe number of reported burglaries and
OL,13,Fdrug offences but there were fewer
OL,14,Fpublic order offences, frauds and
OL,15,Frobberies.
