OL,6,FChief Officer Damian Kitchen, Head of
OL,7,FLaw Enforcement, said: "The activity
OL,8,Fdetailed in this report requires the
OL,9,Fdedication and professionalism of
OL,10,Fgreat people, committed to serving
OL,11,Ftheir community.
OL,13,F"Of course, there are areas in which
OL,14,Fwe can improve, and that work has
OL,15,Fstarted at pace in recent months."
